init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the “Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The government quickly came up with a plan to send the Lost Generations to a remote island in the Pacific Ocean.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The island is called “The Island of Immortality" and it is the only place in the world that has the drug.

actions.name: text-delete

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and it is the only place where the Lost Generations can live.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The island is a place where the Lost Generations can live out the rest of their lives in peace.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The island is a place where they can be free from the government and the world.

actions.text: The affected are the people that received the drug and are now immortal.

actions.text: The government will not be able to provide for the Lost Generations for the rest of their lives.
